## Before contacting support

- Make sure you are using the latest version of the App.
- Include your device model and iOS version.
- Describe the issue and steps to reproduce it.
- Attach screenshots if helpful.

## Common topics

- Profile and resume import issues
- Interview prep plans and session feedback
- Job listings and document tailoring
- Permissions (camera, microphone, photos, notifications)
- Clearing data or reinstalling the App

## Response time

